comments: Easily the best teacher I have ever had in college. Very random and a little bonkers but he respects you and expects high quality work. Make no mistake though, if you want the A, it is very easy to get with him. Show up to class, rock out with him before class starts, listen to his funny stories, turn in quality paper at semester\'s end. Bam! A.

Fun guy. His approach to class is random YouTube videos and a couple papers. Most people in ENG 205 are there because they already took AP English. We all clearly knew how to write and he respected that. He was really laid-back in class but expected high-quality work. He was always willing to provide constructive criticism for assignments.
Literally, by far the sickest instructor I\'ve ever had.
Webster is by far the greatest english teacher i have ever had.

He?s an awesome teacher. He tells you exactly what he wants and if you go above and beyond that he?ll love you. If you give him exactly what he asks for you?ll still get an A. Make sure you go to him with rough drafts when he gives you the opportunity, it?ll definitely help!
Webster is AMAZING! He\'s nuts, but in a good way. Always willing to give advice and very accepting of opinions and ideologies. TAKE HIS CLASSES.

This guy is amazing. Don\'t let the first day scare you off. He is super weird and crazy at first. Actually, he stays pretty crazy, But he gets more awesome as time goes on. Very realistic, outgoing, and has it out for "The Man".

SUUUUUPER CHILL! had to retake ENG105 and got brent, he gives a light workload as long as everyone does the work and comes to class. I missed the first essay and it hurt significantly, but I rewrote it at the end of the semester and got out with an A! just show him you\'re trying and it will srsly go a long way!

Webster is awesome! He\'s one of the sickest professors ever. I walked in and he was playing the Misfits on youtube. His class is pretty easy, he gives a light workload, and it\'s really chill. TAKE HIS CLASS

He is awesome! Not the average college professor, but a lot of fun. He makes the class more enjoyable. He isn\'t afraid to share his opinions, but his somewhat crazy personality makes him an awesome professor. And he really knows what he is talking about!
Awesome professor! He\'s different than all the other professors. Very kool, fun, and CRAZY. Doesn\'t give a lot of work but still keeps us busy. Very clear and helpful :)

Pretty awesome crazy teacher! Makes every class memorable and wants you to succeed. Gives you a lot of time for your essays and help which is very useful. Take this class if you want to learn how to write college essays and like rock music.. and a good laugh
